Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，你的脚没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有点扭伤而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.48,0:01:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会痛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不会痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是医生说，我不能参加马拉松大赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.76,0:01:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.53,0:01:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我这样就能专心拍小樱跑步的英姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.24,0:01:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.62,0:01:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,000)}第21话 小樱的漫长马拉松大赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱跑得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后天的马拉松大赛，今年也是小樱冠军吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.79,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的马拉松大赛，冠亚军是小狼跟我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.53,0:02:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在香港的学校都是小狼跟我跑得最快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.35,0:02:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们班大概能拿到冠亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼你跑得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.99,0:02:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次马拉松大赛，冠亚军非我们莫属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃也很会长跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.14,0:02:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在问谁很会长跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.74,0:03:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会被我远远抛在后面边跑边哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我为什么要哭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心的哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是莓铃你有跑过长跑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们跟刚才那组一样跑五圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要考虑到自己的体力跑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，就位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.71,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.81,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.75,0:03:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到我的速度，现在大概被吓到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.91,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.85,0:04:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃，你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是今天身体不舒服而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前赛跑从来没输给小狼以外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你赛跑不是只有跑过100公尺吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100公尺跟马拉松跑法完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?不都是赛跑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.04,0:05:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能跑得像小樱跟山崎那么快呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是练习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.41,0:05:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马拉松在高地练习效果最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高地是指高山吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.09,0:05:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般马拉松选手都在富士山那种高山上练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.09,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界最高峰也是\N被练习中的马拉松选手第一个征服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是友枝町没有高山啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.17,0:05:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一流的马拉松选手，原来也是一流的登山家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山崎又开始骗人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过练习还是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,练跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.82,0:06:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.96,0:06:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，小樱，这个礼拜五有马拉松大赛是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去年拿到冠军吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们那个年级是几点开始?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午休后马上开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?那我也去看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.34,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天我们只有半天课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥也会来看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们同班，所以他也没课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在哪里跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.22,0:06:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先是跑一圈操场，然后进企鹅公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.46,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出公园后在樱花树大道折返
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后经过图书馆旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再经由公园回学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满长的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说来回有2.5公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很喜欢跑步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，因为你每天都在练习啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每天早上不是都全力冲刺跑到学校吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边喊着"我又睡过头了"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.32,0:07:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪也很佩服你呢\N他说连骑脚踏车都会被你追上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去练马拉松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好别练了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.13,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，你不想跟我一起抵达终点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.74,0:07:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃小姐，饭后最好不要做激烈运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.08,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子会痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才不会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体会着凉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，要有"吸吸哈哈"的节奏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.75,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有最好再跑慢一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑慢一点?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把力气留到终点前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.02,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到终点，再全力一口气冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，温伯，我会试看看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你谢谢小狼少爷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小狼少爷叫我教莓铃小姐长跑的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4年级的领先者进场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.19,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领先者是2班的李小狼跟李莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.73,0:09:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.41,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼跟莓铃先后抵达终点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友枝小学马拉松大赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气也很好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:10:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我跟先前的我完全不同，我已经重生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟得上我的速度吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像很有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道她有什么策略吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.48,0:10:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要努力喔，我会拼命为你加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.39,0:10:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4年级同学请到起跑点集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.62,0:10:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们到折返点等你们，加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.29,0:10:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑到一半跌倒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.88,0:10:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始你别跑太快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了折返点再加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我们要拿到冠亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.05,0:11:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.63,0:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边的情况如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，这里是友枝町上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天睛，气温微低\N微风吹拂，是跑马拉松的好日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.91,0:11:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.98,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想见面，不能见，无奈的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领先的怎么会是臭小鬼跟臭丫头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱在干什么?还不快超越他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.55,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不能说，又想说，一再错过机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.86,0:12:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好想，好想，两人一起飞翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.77,0:12:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想漫步于天际，齐唱着梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我都不觉得累，看来练习的效果出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.94,0:12:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}来吧!抓住你!抓住你!抓住我!抓住我!等一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟小狼一起跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}看着我，说喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.55,0:12:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}对了!遇到你真好，见到你真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.42,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我的思念飞向飞向飞向你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不迷惑地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.54,0:12:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}来吧!抓住你!抓住你!抓住我!抓住我!等一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.78,0:12:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}看着我，说喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.81,0:12:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个角度太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}对了!遇到你真好，见到你真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.97,0:13:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上空的小可，现在是谁领先呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.52,0:13:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不会输给任何人，我是世界上最最最最
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼，他的后面是臭丫头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱是第三名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不到，没办法，只好到公园等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的速度会不会太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度的确很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样后半段会累死喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪子，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，追上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.90,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不觉得奇怪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们跑过折返点已经很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却没有看到对面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定是跑得太慢了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该没离这么远才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.38,0:15:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概因为我跟小狼跑得太快了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有个电灯泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快到了，现在应该已经抢到第一了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱他们在我面前经过两次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.97,0:15:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说他们应该已经折返了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.91,0:15:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们两次都是从相同方向跑来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.38,0:16:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这条路有这么长吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样没办法跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师会骑脚踏车跟在后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫老师载你回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.06,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要，我要跟小狼拿冠亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.53,0:16:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我一起等好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.27,0:16:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜，听说老师已经走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.51,0:16:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是老师应该会跟最后的同学一起回学校吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.94,0:16:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.61,0:17:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才老师好像已经\N跟最后的奈绪子一起离开这条路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.82,0:17:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这张海报我好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.43,0:17:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你们朝着相同方向，重复跑了两趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛牌搞的鬼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到库洛牌的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确能感觉到库洛牌的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.81,0:17:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该就在附近才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.19,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.86,0:17:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"环牌(loop)"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，是环牌搞的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它把你们跑的樱花大道变成了环圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是库洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们什么也没看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不解开环圈的话，它不会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就找不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算看不到也有办法能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这时候也带着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.09,0:18:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.96,0:18:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.86,0:18:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉帝有敕神砚四方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.09,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金木水火土，雷风雷电神敕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.10,0:18:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻磨霹雳电光转，急急如律令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，你在感动个什么劲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去找啊，在路上某处应该有个接点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要切断接点，环牌就会出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.02,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接点?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上一定会有个不对劲的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.69,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话虽是这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里会有接点?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.59,0:19:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.06,0:19:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.10,0:19:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快找个东西把它切断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等环牌出现后，趁它还没接上前立刻封印它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么切断啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕴藏黑暗力量的钥匙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显现真正的神力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.52,0:19:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据契约，小樱命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除封印!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“剑”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复你原来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.14,0:20:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼比较快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是小狼比较快耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱他们怎么这么慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会不会跑错路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.80,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样说也没用啊，你根本没办法跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.14,0:21:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她在一起，你待会再来接她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟她们一起等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小狼要拿冠亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.42,0:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.89,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4年级最后的选手回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家掌声鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.23,0:22:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.16,0:22:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.54,0:22:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是因为我受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.27,0:22:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能发挥实力，绝对能赢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.21,0:22:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.94,0:22:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那张库洛牌，本来也是小狼找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.58,0:22:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有比赛，我绝对绝对要打败你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.52,0:22:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小狼要拿冠亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.32,0:22:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜负现在才开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.79,0:22:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你伤脑筋时的表情也很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.96,0:22:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会输你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.12,0:24:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,300)}包在小可身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这集介绍臭丫头的道服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.98,0:24:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭丫头好像也有一套道服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.05,0:24:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长长的袖子下有个铃当跟小鬼是一套的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.52,0:24:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊，连胸前的刺绣都跟小鬼一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.09,0:24:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裤装方便行动\N适合接近交战，不过重要的是个人功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.03,0:24:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟小鬼那时一样\N我还是一视同仁的为她介绍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.57,0:24:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是个名主持人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.44,0:24:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.81,0:24:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸为了准备研讨会，每天都熬夜很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.74,0:24:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我送东西去爸爸的大学慰劳他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.81,0:24:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?为什么大家都在睡觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.42,0:24:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.32,0:24:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“小樱的好爸爸”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.65,0:24:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也与小樱一起解除封印!
